## Git Settings
# text=auto : All files are checked into the repo with LF line endings
# eol=lf    : Files are checked out using LF locally
* text=auto  eol=lf

# Images are considered binary
*.jpg binary
*.mp4 binary
*.pdf binary
*.png binary
*.svg binary

# Marks the file types as text and specify line endings
*.html text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.scss text eol=lf
*.txt text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
